s simulation game|Business simulation]]\n| [[Sports Interactive]]\n| [[Sega]]\n| {{dts|November 19, 2019|format=mdy}}\n| {{dts|November 18, 2019|format=mdy}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''Get Packed'' \u2020\n| {{Unknown}}\n| Moonshine Studios\n| Coatsink\n| {{TBA}}\n| {{TBA}}<!--{{dts|XXXX-XX-XX|format=mdy}}-->\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Gods and Monsters (video game)|Gods and Monsters]]''<ref>{{cite tweet |user=GoogleStadia |number=1138853471170547714 |date=12 June 2019 |title=#GodsandMonsters, the new adventure game from the creators of Assassin's Creed Odyssey, is coming to Stadia! #UbiE3}}</ref>\n| [[Action-adventure game|Action-adventure]]\n| Ubisoft Quebec\n| [[Ubisoft]]\n| {{TBA}}\n| {{TBA}}<!--{{dts|XXXX-XX-XX|format=mdy}}-->\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Grid (2019 video game)|Grid]]'' #\n| [[Racing video game|Racing]]\n| [[Codemasters]]\n| [[Codemasters]]\n| {{dts|November 19, 2019|format=mdy}}\n| {{dts|11 October 2019|format=mdy}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''Gunsport''\n| [[Sports]], [[Co-op]]\n| [[Necrosoft Games]]\n| [[Necrosoft Games]]\n| {{TBA}}\n| {{TBA}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''Gylt'' \u2020 #\n| {{Unknown}}\n| [[Tequila Works]]\n| {{Unknown}}\n| {{dts|November 19, 2019|format=mdy}}\n| {{dts|November 19, 2019|format=mdy}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Just Dance 2020]]''\n| [[Rhythm game|Rhythm]]\n| [[Ubisoft Paris]]\n| [[Ubisoft]]\n| {{dts|November 19, 2019|format=mdy}}\n| {{dts|2019-11-05|format=mdy}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''Just Shapes And Beats''\n| [[Shoot Em Up]], [[Rhythm]]\n| Berserk Studio\n| Berserk Studio\n| {{TBA}}\n| {{dts|May 31, 2018||}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Kine (video game)|Kine]]''<ref name=\"stadia FAQ games list\">{{cite web |url=https://support.google.com/stadia/answer/9363495?hl=en&ref_topic=9339018 |title=Games on Stadia |author=<!--Not stated--> |date= |website=Stadia Help |publisher=[[Google]] |access-date=2019-09-15}}</ref>\n| [[Puzzle video game|Puzzle]]\n| Gwen Frey\n| Gwen Frey\n| {{dts|November 19, 2019|format=mdy}}\n| {{dts