ate=2019-01-01 |df=mdy-all |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226181813/https://www.theverge.com/2018/10/8/17950998/google-project-stream-gaming-assasins-creed-odyssey-first-impression |archive-date=December 26, 2018 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"HighlyTechno\">{{cite web |last1=Techno |first1=Highly |title=Google\u2019s Stadia Gaming Platform |url=https://highlytechno.com/googles-stadia-gaming-platform-price-specifications/ |website=HighlyTechno |publisher=Shubham |accessdate=20 March 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Stadia\">{{cite web |last1=Techno |first1=Highly |title=Google\u2019s Stadia Gaming Platform |url=https://store.google.com/product/stadia_founders_edition |website=store.google.com |publisher=Mayur |accessdate=6 June 2019}}</ref>\n}}\n\n== Further reading ==\n\n{{refbegin}}\n* {{Cite web |last1=Armstrong |first1=Stephen |title=Inside Google Stadia |work=[[Wired UK]] |date=2019-10-04 |url=https://www.wired.co.uk/article/google-stadia |accessdate=2019-10-05 |df=mdy-all }}\n* {{Cite web |last1=Campbell |first1=Colin |last2=Plante |first2=Chris |title=Google Stadia: Phil Harrison answers our biggest questions |work=[[Polygon (website)|Polygon]] |date=2019-03-20 |url=https://www.polygon.com/2019/3/20/18274811/google-stadia-interview-phil-harrison-gdc-2019 |accessdate=2019-03-23 |df=mdy-all }}\n* {{Cite web |last1=Carpenter |first1=Nicole |title=Google Stadia will launch without a bunch of promised features |work=[[Polygon (website)|Polygon]] |date=2019-11-13 |url=https://www.polygon.com/2019/11/13/20963561/google-stadia-launch-day-promises-ama |language=en-US |accessdate=2019-11-14 |df=mdy-all }}\n* {{Cite web |last1=Grey |first1=Jess |title=Stadia Might Be One of Google's Best Products\u2014Eventually |work=[[Wired (magazine)|Wired]] |date=2019-11-18 |url=https://www.wired.com/review/google-stadia/ |accessdate=2019-11-22 |df=mdy-all }}\n* {{Cite web |last1=Hollister |first1=Sean |title=Google\u2019s Stadia cloud gaming service is coming No